hzrt iimaam saahb kii drgaah pr log duur duur se apnii muraade lekr aate haiN . yh allaah ke nek bnde haiN .

jhiNjhaanaa ksbe kaa naam raajaa jhiNjjhiNj ke naam pr pddaa haiN .
bhut saal pehle raajaa jhiNjjhiNj yhaaN ke logoN pr khuub julm
krtaa thaa . jb bhii koii ldddhkii shaadii hone ke baad ksbe se baahr
jaatii thii yaa bhu bnkr ksbe me aatii thii to sbse pehle use raajaa jhiNjjhiNj ke drbaar me pesh honaa pdddhtaa thaa . ek raat raja uskii ijjaat nilaam krtaa thaa . ksbe me aisaa koii bhaadur laal nhiiN thaa jo raajaa ke julm ko rok ske . raajaa khuub apnii mnmaanii kr rhaa thaa . jb julm hd se jyaadaa brhne lge to uupr vaalaa apne kisii nek bnde ko bhejkr julm ko roktaa hai.
ab iimaam saahb ke ustaad jo jhiNjhaanaa ksbe ke hii the unhone preshaan hokr apne cele iimaam saahb ko kht likhkr saarii
daastaan btaayii . iimaam saahb ne kht pddhkr apnii maaN se apnaa duudh maaph kraa kr jhiNjhaanaa ksbe ke lie ghr se nikl gye or yhaaN aakr raajaa jhiNjjhiNj se lddaayii lddii or usko ktl kr diyaa . khud bhii shhiid ho gye aur bhut saare log shhiid ho gye . tb jaakr jhiNjhaanaa ksbe ke logoN ne
raajaa jhiNjjhiNj ke julm se nijaat paayii .
iimaam saahb ne apnii zindaagii ko allaah ke lie kurbaan kr dii . naa shaadii , naa dolt aur naa ghr sb kuch chodddh diyaa sirph allaah ke vaaste .
yhii log allaa ke nek aur scce bnde haiN inke vjh se hii duniyaa gulzaar haiN .

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
People come to the Dargah of Hazrat Imam Sahib from far away places with their wishes. These are righteous servants of Allah.

Jhinjhana town is named after King Jhinjhinj.
Many years ago, King Jhinjhinj oppressed the people of this place.
used to do . Whenever a girl goes out of the town after getting married
If she went to the town or came to the town as a daughter-in-law, then first of all she had to appear in the court of King Jhinjhinj. One night the king used to praise him. There was no brave man in the town who could stop the king's atrocities. The king was doing his own thing a lot. When oppression starts increasing beyond limits, God stops the oppression by sending one of His pious servants.
Now Imam Sahib's teacher, who was from Jhinjhana town, got upset and wrote a letter to his disciple Imam Sahib,
Told the story. After reading the letter, Imam Sahib got his mother to give up his milk and left home for Jhinjhana town and after coming here, he fought with King Jhinjhinj and killed him. He himself was martyred and many people were martyred. Then the people of Jhinjhana town
Got relief from the oppression of King Jhinjhinj.
Imam Sahib sacrificed his life for Allah. Neither marriage, nor wealth, nor home, left everything only for the sake of Allah.
These people are the pious and true servants of Allah and it is because of them that the world is prosperous.
